<span id="Description"></span>
== Описание ==

<div lang="en" dir="ltr" class="mw-content-ltr">
The [[Image:BIM_Leader.svg|24px]] [[BIM_Leader|BIM Leader]] tool creates a leader line, a '''Wire''' object with an arrow symbol at the last selected point. The tool is supposed to be used in conjunction with the [[BIM_Text|BIM Text]] tool to create annotations in BIM projects.
</div>

<div lang="en" dir="ltr" class="mw-content-ltr">
==Usage==
</div>

<div lang="en" dir="ltr" class="mw-content-ltr">
# There are several ways to invoke the tool:
#* Press the {{Button|[[Image:BIM_Leader.svg|16px]] [[BIM_Leader|Leader]]}} button.
#* Select the {{MenuCommand|Annotation → [[Image:BIM_Leader.svg|16px]] Leader}} option from the menu.
#* Use the keyboard shortcut: {{KEY|L}} then {{KEY|E}}.
# The {{MenuCommand|Leader}} task panel opens.
# Pick the first point in the [[3D_View|3D View]], or type coordinates and press the {{Button|[[Image:Draft_AddPoint.svg|16px]] Enter Point}} button.
# Pick additional points in the [[3D_View|3D View]], or type coordinates and press the {{Button|[[Image:Draft_AddPoint.svg|16px]] Enter Point}} button.
# Press {{KEY|Esc}} or the {{Button|Close}} button to finish the tool.
</div>

<div lang="en" dir="ltr" class="mw-content-ltr">
==Notes==
</div>

<div lang="en" dir="ltr" class="mw-content-ltr">
This tool is based on [[Draft_Wire|Draft Wire]].
</div>


